Notebook[{
Cell["CompleteInfraEquilateralTriangle", "Title",ExpressionUUID->"fdceb050-2476-4ad9-947d-9bf52d8c3625"],

Cell["[LLM Generated]", "Subtitle",ExpressionUUID->"b51a9148-053f-4ef9-a484-d067545139c3"],

Cell["\<\
CompleteInfraEquilateralTriangle[g, p1, p2] returns the apex vertices c satisfying \
d(c, p1) == d(c, p2) == d(p1, p2) (Euclid I.1). Returns a List of unary \
InfraPoint[{c}] wrappers; n / UpTo[n] / All control multiplicity. Option \
Method (\"Metric\" (default); \"Spectral\", \"Resistance\" reserved).\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"9bccf76f-8f29-47af-a374-c53dad4159e7"],

